Description: A collection of methods for commonly undertaken analytical tasks, 
    primarily developed for Public Health Scoltand (PHS) analysts, but the package is also 
    generally useful to others working in the healthcare space, particularly since it has
    functions for working with Community Health Index (CHI) numbers. 
    The package can help to make data manipulation and analysis more 
    efficient and reproducible.
